iffen]]<br />(Vikings)\n| [[Ryan Allen (American football)|Ryan Allen]]<br />(Patriots)\n| [[Dustin Hopkins]]<br />([[Washington Redskins|Redskins]])\n|- style=\"background:#ffffbf;\" \n|'''Sept.'''<ref>{{cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/Players-of-the-Month---September.aspx |title=Players of the Month \u2013 September |website=Nflcommunications.com |accessdate=2016-12-23 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022190736/https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/Players-of-the-Month---September.aspx |archivedate=October 22, 2016 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| [[LeGarrette Blount]]<br />([[New England Patriots|Patriots]])\n| [[Matt Ryan (American football)|Matt Ryan]]<br />([[Atlanta Falcons|Falcons]])\n| Von Miller<br />(Broncos)\n| [[Fletcher Cox]]<br />([[Philadelphia Eagles|Eagles]])\n| [[Justin Tucker]]<br />([[Baltimore Ravens|Ravens]])\n| Dustin Hopkins<br />(Redskins)\n|-\n!4<ref>{{cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-5-.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week \u2013 Week 4 |website=Nflcommunications.com |accessdate=2016-09-28 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106102457/https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-5-.aspx |archivedate=January 6, 2017 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| [[Ben Roethlisberger]]<br />(Steelers)\n| [[Julio Jones]]<br />(Falcons)\n| [[Zach Brown]]<br />([[Buffalo Bills|Bills]])\n| [[Aaron Donald]]<br />([[Los Angeles Rams|Rams]])\n| [[Will Fuller]]<br />([[Houston Texans|Texans]])\n| [[Jon Ryan]]<br />([[Seattle Seahawks|Seahawks]])\n|-\n!5<ref>{{cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-5---.aspx |title=AFC and NFC Players of the Week \u2013 Week 5 |website=Nflcommunications.com |accessdate=2016-09-28 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106102357/https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-5---.aspx |arch