17 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| Le\u2019Veon Bell<br />(Steelers)\n| Aaron Rodgers<br />(Packers)\n| [[Quintin Demps]]<br />(Texans)\n| Vic Beasley<br />(Falcons)\n| Tyreek Hill<br />(Chiefs)\n| Johnny Hekker<br />(Rams)\n|-\n!17<ref>{{cite web |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-17-.aspx |title=AFC & NFC Players of the Week \u2013 Week 17 |website=Nflcommunications.com |accessdate=2017-01-05 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106102807/https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/AFC-and-NFC-Players-of-the-Week---Week-17-.aspx |archivedate=January 6, 2017 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n| [[Julian Edelman]]<br />(Patriots)\n| Matt Ryan<br />(Falcons)\n| [[Robert Mathis]]<br />([[Indianapolis Colts|Colts]])\n| [[Dominique Rodgers-Cromartie]]<br />(Giants)\n| Tyreek Hill<br />(Chiefs)\n| [[Bryan Anger]]<br />(Buccaneers)\n|}\n\n{| border=0\n|- valign=\"top\" \n| \n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%; text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!Week\n!FedEx Air<br />Player of the Week<br />(Quarterbacks)<ref name=\"FedEx\">{{cite web |url=http://www.nfl.com/voting/players-air-and-ground/2016 |title=FedEx Players Air and Ground |website=NFL.com |accessdate=2016-12-23 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023210813/http://www.nfl.com/voting/players-air-and-ground/2016 |archivedate=October 23, 2016 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n!FedEx Ground<br />Player of the Week<br />(Running Backs)<ref name=\"FedEx\" />\n!Pepsi Next<br />Rookie of the Week<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nfl.com/voting/rookies/2016/ |title=Pepsi Rookie of the WEEK |website=NFL.com |accessdate=2016-12-23 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223151123/http://www.nfl.com/voting/rookies/2016 |archivedate=December 23, 2016 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n!Castrol Edge<br />Clutch Performer<br />of the Week<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nfl.com/voting/clutch-performer/2016/ |title=Castrol Edge Clutch Performer of the Week |website=NFL.