16 All-Pro Team}}\n\nThe following players were named First Team All-Pro by the [[Associated Press]]:\n\n{| border=0\n|- valign=\"top\" \n| \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Offense\n|-\n|[[Quarterback]]||[[Matt Ryan (American football)|Matt Ryan]], [[2016 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta]]\n|-\n|[[Running back]]||[[Ezekiel Elliott]], [[2016 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas]]\n|-\n|[[Offensive backfield|Flex]]||[[David Johnson (running back)|David Johnson]], [[2016 Arizona Cardinals season|Arizona]]\n|-\n|[[Wide receiver]]||[[Antonio Brown]], [[2016 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh]]<br />[[Julio Jones]], [[2016 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta]]\n|-\n|[[Tight end]]||[[Travis Kelce]], [[2016 Kansas City Chiefs season|Kansas City]]\n|-\n|[[Offensive tackle|Left tackle]]||[[Tyron Smith]], [[2015 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas]]\n|-\n|[[Guard (American football)|Left guard]]||[[Kelechi Osemele]], [[2016 Oakland Raiders season|Oakland]]\n|-\n|[[Center (American football)|Center]]||[[Travis Frederick]], [[2016 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas]]\n|-\n|[[Guard (American football)|Right guard]]||[[Zack Martin]], [[2016 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas]]\n|-\n|[[Offensive tackle|Right tackle]]||[[Jack Conklin]], [[2016 Tennessee Titans season|Tennessee]]\n|-\n|}\n|  style=\"padding-left:40px;\" |\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Defense\n|-\n|[[Defensive end|Edge rusher]]||[[Khalil Mack]], [[2016 Oakland Raiders season|Oakland]]<br />[[Vic Beasley]], [[2016 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta]]\n|-\n|[[Defensive tackle|Interior lineman]]||[[Aaron Donald]], [[2016 Los Angeles Rams season|Los Angeles]]<br />[[Damon Harrison]], [[2016 New York Giants season|New York Giants]]\n|-\n|[[Linebacker]]||[[Von Miller]], [[2016 Denver Broncos season|Denver]]<br />[[Bobby Wagner]], [[2016 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle]]<br />[[Sean Lee]], [[2016 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas]]\n|-\n|[[Cornerback]]||[[Aqib Talib]], [[2016 Denver Broncos season|Denver]]<br />[[Marcus Peters]], [[2016 